                   </h2>
                  </div>
                 </li>
                 <li class="last expanded" data-link-order="1" data-menu-group="seminars" data-menu-location="main-menu-2">
                  <div class="col-2">
                   <h2>
                    <a class="heading-link" href="/seminars/endowed-special-lectures/thomas-w-leland-jr-lecture-chemical-engineering" title="">
                     Endowed &amp; Special Lectures
                    </a>
                    <ul class="menu">
                     <li class="first leaf" data-menu-group="endowed-special-lectures" data-menu-location="main-menu-3">
                      <a href="/seminars/endowed-special-lectures/thomas-w-leland-jr-lecture-chemical-engineering">
                       Thomas W. Leland, Jr.
                      </a>
                     </li>
                     <li class="leaf" data-menu-group="endowed-special-lectures" data-menu-location="main-menu-3">
                      <a href="/seminars/endowed-special-lectures/paul-c-wilber-lectureship">
                       Paul C. Wilber
                      </a>
                     </li>
                     <li class="last leaf" data-menu-group="endowed-special-lectures" data-menu-location="main-menu-3">
                      <a href="/seminars/endowed-special-lectures/chevron-lecture-energy">
                       Chevron Lecture
                      </a>
                     </li>
                    </ul>
                   </h2>
                  </div>
                 </li>
                 <div class="col-4">
                  <p>
                   The Department of Chemical and Biomolecular Engineering holds regular seminars, with speakers from academia and industry. Endowed lectures further enrich life in the department by bringing in speakers who are leaders in the field and experts in their areas. Watch the department calendar for all seminar listings.
                  </p>
                 </div>
                 <div class="col-3 omega">
